item.title: Need help with Webclient! [317]
item.dc:creator: @snipeman32 snipeman32
item.description:
@snipeman32 wrote:

EDIT- Oh you have a delta source, i used the exact same source as you. go to rswebclients.com make an account, then click create a webclient. When it asks what source or loader base you have (not sure what the option is called), choose bluur. they dont have a selta option yet but the bluur option works for it as of right now. you have to host your server yourself hough. so you need to keep your CPU up 24/7 to keep your server up 24/7. Pm me when you get it up cause i’d love the Admin position.
